{"tid":1191487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁愛詩：修例被政治妖魔化　望通過後爭議平息","createTime":"2019-06-08T03:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T17:11:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2daf029c4528f636414bbc3688ea9527053fce3a","tid":1191487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190608/s00001/0fd597d0ae7988be54ac1d123d219722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190608%2Fs00001%2F0fd597d0ae7988be54ac1d123d219722.jpg&h=85cc7012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂觸動爭議，前律政司長梁愛詩在香港電台今早（8日）播出的節目《香港家書》稱，今次修例「本來不是一件複雜的事情」，「被政治化和妖魔化」，「希望通過立法程式後，社會的爭議能夠平息」。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩批評，「當年逃犯條例通過，以及立法會審議每一個長期移交逃犯協議時，有誰提出條例所列的人權保障沒有實質意義，沒有足夠地保障逃犯的人權呢？」<br />\n<br />\n她續稱，今次修例建議2月已經公布，「這四個月期間在民間、立法會和社群都有密集的討論，政府官員、學者和社團都就問題作講解，政府吸收了市民的建議，答應作出合理的修改，立法會將會審議草案，我認為整個過程將有充分的討論而不是草草了事。」"},{"pid":"6fb66f7fe748b80ffe4ccc0b8b855f1afa096e39","tid":1191487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190608/s00001/1559958778132/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190608%2Fs00001%2F1559958778132%2F&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW89jJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=fd74299a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190608%2Fs00001%2F1559958778132%2F&h=748bc201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190608/s00001/1559958778132/</a>"},{"pid":"ed5b8b95280fad55e09e09a6f079dda022d2ecf9","tid":1191487,"uid":168366,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:17:07.000Z","msg":"就係對支那司法完全無信心呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"c875e401930d1ff982cfa732d90ad50a1c540bc2","tid":1191487,"uid":9694,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"r